rComments: Dan is friendly and eccentric.  He's an interesting lecturer who always tries to involve the class in discussion and debates that were awesome.  The two papers are graded tough, but he offers so much extra credit it hardly matters.  A fun and interesting class -- I recommend it!

He's a great teacher who knows his stuff. Very opinionated about things and isn't afraid to show it. The class involves posts and comments online, he grades the midterm hard. But claims that the final won't be as bad
